{"tid":2432572,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日有冇必要裝防毒軟件？有 Common sense就夠？","createTime":"2021-03-04T12:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T11:02:17.000Z","uid":156109,"like":8,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"438e13b4f8f55b5cb9e57e5ec52234e2f7dbaf8f","tid":2432572,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"好多人話有 common sense就夠<br />\n唔好亂上網 小心啲<br />\n從來冇中過毒<br />\nWindows Defender夠做 <br />\n同人講話用防毒會俾人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但問題係中咗毒邊有咁易知道<br />\n仲要依家咁多 phishing sites<br />\n唔覺意入錯假網站輸入咗敏感資料就係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有用過 anti virus就知 即使係上連登之類嘅正常網都可以照樣自動連上去 phishing site <br />\n或者係任何可疑 connection"},{"pid":"53f4ddadd5046da4712ebcf689d11d289d49fd99","tid":2432572,"uid":156109,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T12:14:37.000Z","msg":"呢個人因為 google search到假網站 冇留意<br />\n就俾人偷晒啲 cryptocurrency<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kZI2OTtkdGY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkZI2OTtkdGY&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=f95b4963\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kZI2OTtkdGY</a>"},{"pid":"968791d4e620e74366dbfaff698c0a2ee8834f44","tid":2432572,"uid":366509,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:37:07.000Z","msg":"所以要bookmark晒所有同錢有關既網<br />\n就算收到email都用返自己bookmark條link去上<br />\n同埋有得用手機app就用手機app, 因為APP商店關係,真係防到好多野<br />\n<br />\n我自己就bookmark左銀行link,轉錢過錢同手機 App"},{"pid":"9e52b22f412c2f53f1ff668114a8781ec47effc2","tid":2432572,"uid":62259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:38:27.000Z","msg":"裝囉<br />\n又唔係好大容量"},{"pid":"44943bb49c676e3a8800d39d0c6ccf9a6e33548f","tid":2432572,"uid":227788,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"set dns 1.1.1.2好過用防毒,<br />\n1.1.1.3仲可以有益身心 人都健康D"},{"pid":"059005e445d86c6fd